div.div:
Refactor core functionalities for economy and essentials features
Removed WarpBuilder and deprecated features like CHEQUE payment type. Simplified inventory clear logic with new EssentialsSubscriber. Enhanced messaging system using NoticeWrapper for better flexibility. Integrated new economy service utilities and streamlined transfer logic for improved maintainability.

Refactor: Consolidate and restructure item-related imports and packets
Moved `item` related classes into a unified `items` package for better organization and consistency. Additionally, restructured clan-related packets into a `clan.packet` subpackage. Removed unused `custom-items` plugin dependencies from various modules, cleaning up build files.

Refactor: Consolidate and restructure item-related imports and packets
Moved `item` related classes into a unified `items` package for better organization and consistency. Additionally, restructured clan-related packets into a `clan.packet` subpackage. Removed unused `custom-items` plugin dependencies from various modules, cleaning up build files.

Refactor message handling and combat logic integration
Replaced `MessageWrapper` with `NoticeWrapper` and `TextWrapper` for simplified message handling. Integrated combat logic into duels and adjusted item drop handling to rely on `CombatLogConfig`. Removed unused dependencies and improved code reuse by consolidating constants and utilities.
